From 8acc5eb5e9a6659aa512df4bd51a050840d7ec54 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Wed, 13 May 2026 20:51:19 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Add firmware Wi-Fi manager component

Introduce clawcam_wifi_manager as the dedicated firmware component for STA
connection management. It exposes SSID/password configuration plus a
provisioning-mode flag via Kconfig, applies a connect timeout and retry
policy, and reports connection health (status string, RSSI, retry count,
last connect duration) for diagnostics.

main.c now consults the Wi-Fi manager before any gateway upload attempt;
SD-card media, metadata, and event-JSON persistence run unconditionally so
the offline source of truth is independent of network success. When Wi-Fi
is disabled, in provisioning mode, or fails to associate within the
configured timeout/retry budget, the upload is skipped and the firmware
continues with SD-only behavior.
